text: A Rumor of Love (also known as The Love Rumor; , translit. Eshaet Hob or Ishayat hub) is a 1960 Egyptian romantic comedy movie directed by Fatin Abdel Wahab and starring Omar Sharif, Soad Hosny, Youssef Wahbi, Ehsan Sherif, Gamal Ramses. == Other websites == * Category:1960 romantic comedy movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:Movies directed by Fatin Abdel Wahab
title: A Rumor of Love
